snippet.title: Monica's Newlywed Life - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
When Kyle and his party’s adventure comes to an abrupt end, Kyle decides to ask Monica to marry him. Starting a new life in the countryside, they must earn a living, and get to know their new home.
